features: VALUE PACK - 14 pcs Stanley Mug Accessory Set includes 2 Stanley Straw caps, 2 Square Spill Stoppers and 2 Round Lid Leak Stoppers, 1 Cloud Straw Lid and 1 Pink Flower Straw Lid, 1 Silicone Boot, 2 Straws and 1 Straw Brush, 2 Alloy Pendants, Designed to fit Stanley Adventure Quencher 40 oz and Stanley IceFlow 20 oz 30 oz glass water bottles. Straw caps fit 9-10 mm straws.

OUTSTANDING USEFULNESS - The silicone water bottle cover prevents unwanted scratches and dents, is abrasion resistant, non-slip, reduces noise, and extends the life of the bottle. The custom cleaning brush is designed to clean the inside of the straw. Use the attachable straw cover to keep dirt and dust out of the Stanley Cups for easy, healthy use. With the adorable alloy charm hanging from the handle of the Stanley Cup, you'll never confuse your Stanley mug with another one again.

HIGH QUALITY MATERIAL - This water bottle accessory set is made of food grade silicone, which is durable, odorless and reusable. Easy to clean, hand washable and dishwasher safe. Alloy charm accessories are made of high quality hardware with high quality gold lobster clasp chain. Cute flower straw, smiling cloud straw lid and alloy charms make your cup less monotonous and bring you happiness every day.

WIDE COMPATIBILITY - Our spill kit accessories are compatible with Stanley Quencher 1.0/ H2.0 FlowState Stainless Steel Vacuum Insulated Mug 40 oz/ 30 oz. The 10mm straw cap is a perfect match for the original Stanley straw 10mm size. The silicone sleeve is designed to fit the Stanley Adventure Quencher 40 oz H2.0 and Stanley IceFlow 20oz 30oz and Simple Modern 40 oz as well as other cups with a bottom diameter of 2.75-2.95 inches.

WIDE APPLICATIONS - Straw lids are small and portable, suitable for all occasions or outdoor activities, such as walking, camping, hiking.Stanley cup handle with daisy and cloud charm, perfect gift for family, friends, kids, women, girlfriends, etc. on Mother's Day, Birthday, Christmas, Thanksgiving, New Year's Day and other holidays.
